210 (y) "Regional Board Examination" means initial
211 licensure examinations administered by the Western Regional
212 Examining Board (WREB), the North East Regional Board of
213 Dental Examiners (NERB), the Commission on Dental Competency
214 Assessments (CDCA), Council of Interstate Testing Agencies
