217 psychomotor skills;
218 (z) "Repository" means the repository of original
219 documents of a Licensee that may include original
220 transcripts, certification documents, test scores, military
221 training records, previous or current licensing documents
222 and other sources of materials needed for applications and
223 verification administered by the AADB or its successor. The
224 Repository shall receive documents from primary or
